description: This is part of a sound kit i've done in 2002 during a session testing Deconstructor from Tobybear, the basic version was a simple drum-loop, sliced and processed with pitchshifting, panning, tremolo, delay, reverb, vocoder.. and all those cool onboard fx Tweaking here and there the original sound was completely mangled.. i saved the work in 2 folders: 'deconstruction-set' contain the longer slices (meant to be used with a sampler), 'deconstruction-kit' collects the smallest slices (to be used in a drum machine)
name: deconstruction-kit_bip-zip.wav
tags: cuts digital drum-kit fx glitch noise slices soundeffect

description: I was walking through an unknown part of the city near the river, through the neighborhood made out of slums, I have never seen before, in search of...something. Sounds, I guess. I thought he was going to rip me apart, but the fence stopped him from doing that :) So, instead of playing with him I decided to share his angry barking with the world. description: This is part of a sound kit i've done in 2002 during a session testing Deconstructor from Tobybear, the basic version was a simple drum-loop, sliced and processed with pitchshifting, panning, tremolo, delay, reverb, vocoder.. and all those cool onboard fx Tweaking here and there the original sound was completely mangled.. i saved the work in 2 folders: 'deconstruction-set' contain the longer slices (meant to be used with a sampler), 'deconstruction-kit' collects the smallest slices (to be used in a drum machine)
name: deconstruction-kit_snare2.wav
tags: cuts digital drum-kit fx glitch noise slices soundeffect

description: This is part of a sound kit i've done in 2002 during a session testing Deconstructor from Tobybear, the basic version was a simple drum-loop, sliced and processed with pitchshifting, panning, tremolo, delay, reverb, vocoder.. and all those cool onboard fx Tweaking here and there the original sound was completely mangled.. i saved the work in 2 folders: 'deconstruction-set' coontain the longer slices (meant to be used with a sampler), 'deconstruction-kit' collects the smallest slices (to be used in a drum machine)
name: deconstruction-kit_snare3.wav
tags: cuts digital drum-kit fx glitch noise slices soundeffect
